==English==
===Etymology===
From Old English ''scunian''

===Verb===
'''shun'''
#''(transitive)'' [[Avoid]], especially [[persistently]]; to [[exclude]] socially.
#''(transitive)'' [[Escape]] (a threatened evil, an unwelcome task etc).
#''(transitive)'' [[Screen]], hide.
#''(transitive)'' [[Shove]], push.

